== 在任 ==
* 總統: [[卡罗洛斯·帕普利亚斯|卡羅洛斯·帕普利亞斯]] 
* 總理: [[安东尼斯·萨马拉斯|安東尼斯·薩馬拉斯]] 

== 大事紀 ==

=== 5月 ===

* 5月24日 - [[愛琴海|愛琴海]]中發生芮氏規模6.4級的地震<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.worldbulletin.net/turkey/137204/huge-earthquake-rocks-turkey-and-greece|title = Huge earthquake rocks Turkey and Greece-UPDATED|date = 24 May 2014|accessdate = 15 January 2015|archive-date = 2015-07-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150703144422/http://www.worldbulletin.net/turkey/137204/huge-earthquake-rocks-turkey-and-greece|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 11月 ===
* 11月27日 - 希臘工會開始大範圍罷工，以抗議政府的持續緊縮措施，包括公共醫療部門、教育部門、和運輸服務部門等都受到影響<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/general-strike-shuts-down-services-across-greece-114112700427_1.html|title = General strike shuts down services across Greece|date = 27 November 2014|accessdate = 15 January 2015|archive-date = 2015-07-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150704050314/http://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/general-strike-shuts-down-services-across-greece-114112700427_1.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 12月 ===
* 12月23日  - [[2014–15年希腊总统选举|2014–15年希臘總統選舉]]的第二輪投票在今天展開。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/dec/23/greece-presidential-vote-second-round|title = Greek presidential vote goes to third round|date = 23 December 2014|accessdate = 15 January 2015|archive-date = 2015-07-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150706135640/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/dec/23/greece-presidential-vote-second-round|dead-url = no}}</ref>
* 12月28日 - [[義大利|義大利]]籍[[郵輪|郵輪]][[諾曼大西洋號|諾曼大西洋號]]（MS Norman Atlantic），在由[[希臘|希臘]]往義大利途中，於[[科孚島|科孚島]]西北44[[海浬|海浬]]處發生事故起火，已知有150人登上[[救生艇|救生艇]]，乘員總數466人<ref>{{cite news|author=Adam Withnall|title=Norman Atlantic ferry fire: Passengers cry out for help as burning Greece-Italy car ferry is evacuated in high wind and rough seas|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/norman-atlantic-ablaze-major-rescue-under-way-as-greeceitaly-ferry-evacuated-in-high-winds-9946679.html|accessdate=2014-12-28|newspaper=[[獨立報|獨立報]]|date=2014-12-28|language=en|archive-date=2014-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228112901/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/norman-atlantic-ablaze-major-rescue-under-way-as-greeceitaly-ferry-evacuated-in-high-winds-9946679.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=義大利籍郵輪失火 義希海空急救援|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%B1%8D%E9%83%B5%E8%BC%AA%E5%A4%B1%E7%81%AB-%E7%BE%A9%E5%B8%8C%E6%B5%B7%E7%A9%BA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4-113027703.html|accessdate=2014-12-28|newspaper=[[公視新聞|公視新聞]]|date=2014-12-28|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2014-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228141747/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%B1%8D%E9%83%B5%E8%BC%AA%E5%A4%B1%E7%81%AB-%E7%BE%A9%E5%B8%8C%E6%B5%B7%E7%A9%BA%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4-113027703.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

